| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7765 — Recovery Inhibition (kairos)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ec3f6a15-33c8-54dd-82b4-9fb99a9aa7b2"
